item.title: About
item.description: I am a college student studying at Central South University (CSU) in China. I love programming programs, and I hope that I can find myself by programming. I also like to watch Japanese animation. My favorite music is the theme song of PSYCHO-PASS, 名前のない怪物. My hometown is in Taipei, Taiwan.
